org.batfish.datamodel

Class CommunityList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.datamodel.routing_policy.expr.CommunitySetExpr
      • org.batfish.datamodel.CommunityList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class CommunityList
extends CommunitySetExpr
    Represents a named access-list whose matching criteria is restricted to regexes on community attributes sent with a bgp advertisement.
